snippet.title: CountryCide - A Terrifying Grimdark DOOM Total Conversion Mod with Templars & Tentacle Monsters!
snippet.description:
Trench Foot: CountryCide - A Terrifying Grimdark Horror DOOM Total Conversion Mod with Templars & Tentacle Monsters!

Read More & Play CountryCide, Free: https://www.freegameplanet.com/countrycide-doom-total-conversion-mod/

CountryCide is a prequel to the awesome in development Trench Foot mod I covered a couple of years ago. You can check out a playthrough of it here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r1fyTNbf1jQ 

CountryCide ModDB Page: https://www.moddb.com/mods/trench-foot-wip/downloads
